Package org.jmisb.api.klv.st1905

ST 1905 Motion Imagery Metadata (MIMD): Platform.

ST 1901, ST 1902, ST 1903, ST 1904, ST 1905, ST 1906, ST 1907 and ST 1908 collectively define Motion Imagery Metadata (MIMD). The Motion Imagery Metadata (MIMD) Model includes information about platforms that host payloads. ST 1905 defines the modeling information about the different types of platforms and their specific attributes. The platform model includes classes for the Staging system (which is described in ST 1906) and Payloads (which is described in ST 1907).

Implementation note: Most of the implementation of this document is generated from the Motion Imagery Modeling Language (MIML) representation.
